Irate youths burn Sotitobire Miracle Church in Akure. It should be recalled that the church was where a year old boy declared missing. The angry community members set on fire after the corpse of in the church was later found buried at the Church Altar. The Prophet of the church, Babatunde, is currently in the custody of the DSS. Video from TVC below: Just In:
